articles.title: About
articles.contents:
The Statistics Graduate Student Union is a student group at the
University of Toronto which represents graduate students (MSc and PhD)
in the Department of Statistical Sciences. We organize events for our
graduate students and represent their interests to the university. We
have organized the annual Statistics Student Research Day, jointly with
the Department, for the past 12 years.
Contact
Email: sgsudoss[at]gmail.com

articles.title: Statistics Graduate Student Union
articles.description: Welcome to the website of Graduate Student Union at the Department of Statistical Sciences at the University of Toronto.
articles.contents:
News
June 22, 2022: Liam Welsh has been elected President
of the SGSU for the 2022-23 academic year. Liam will begin his term in
July.
April 11, 2022: The 12th annual Statistics Student
Research Day will be held this year on May 25th, 2022. For information
about the event, click here.
